title: The Vegan Violence Problem (Durianrider, Gary Yourofsky & Me)
description:
Anna Scanlon is a vegan who raises difficult questions within veganism.  You can find her channel here: https://www.youtube.com/user/TheAnnainWonderland
Please take the time to see my own (earlier) video, "Against Violence: Against Gary Yourofsky."  The link is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3UKixnfBwMk
